@DATABASE "Con-Quest"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - C - Con-Quest"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - C
                   ====================================

                                 Con-Quest
                                 =========


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Immunity       " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(23225,201)"}                23225,201
@{"Infinite Energy" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(62673,201)"}                62673,201


                         What's the difference between "Immunity" and
                         "Infinite Energy"? Umm.. Nothing at all! I
                         just included it here because I found it :)
                         Actually, one switches off the detection,
                         while the other just stops the energy being
                         drained when you do hit something.


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
